%META:TOPICPARENT{name="WebHome"}%
---+ Keyboard Shortcuts

%TOC%

All shortcuts are single-press, no modifier (except where =Shift= is
noted). Typing into a text field (threshold input, event search,
background-hex input) suppresses the hotkeys until focus leaves the
field. Combinations with =Ctrl=, =Cmd= or =Alt= are reserved for the
browser.

---++ Camera

| *Key*          | *Action*                                       |
| Mouse drag     | Orbit camera                                   |
| Scroll         | Zoom                                           |
| Right-drag     | Pan                                            |
| =R=            | Reset view to the default isometric            |
| =1= / =2= / =3= | Top / side / isometric presets                |

---++ Panels

| *Key*  | *Action*                                                |
| =M=    | Pin / unpin the left (sidebar) panel                    |
| =E=    | Pin / unpin the right (energy threshold) panel          |
| =G=    | Open the ATLAS Ghost envelopes popover                  |
| =S=    | Open the Settings panel                                 |
| =?=    | Open the shortcuts cheat-sheet (inside Settings)        |
| =Esc=  | Close the topmost overlay / exit cinema                 |

---++ Scene toggles

| *Key*     | *Action*                                                |
| =T=       | Toggle TILE sub-detector                                |
| =L= / =A= | Toggle LAr (EMB + EMEC)                                 |
| =H=       | Toggle HEC                                              |
| =F=       | Toggle FCAL                                             |
| =J=       | Toggle reconstructed tracks                             |
| =K=       | Toggle topological clusters                             |
| =Shift+K= | Toggle the cluster-E_T threshold switch                 |
| =I=       | Toggle cell-hover tooltip and outline                   |
| =B=       | Toggle beam-axis indicator                              |
| =V=       | Toggle *All cells* &mdash; fill detectors absent from the XML |
| =Shift+B= | Open the scene-background colour picker                 |
| =Shift+S= | Toggle the cylindrical-wedge slicer gizmo               |
| =C=       | Cinema mode &mdash; hide UI, auto-rotate or guided tour |

---++ Data source

| *Key*          | *Action*                                       |
| =&larr;= / =&rarr;= | Previous / next event in the current list |
| =Space=        | Pause / resume live polling                    |

---++ Output

| *Key*  | *Action*                                                |
| =P=    | Screenshot &mdash; open resolution picker               |
| =/=    | Focus the event-list search box                         |

---++ Slicer gestures

When the slicer is active, the 3D handle at the origin accepts the
following pointer gestures:

| *Gesture*            | *Effect*                                                   |
| Left-drag &mdash; screen-Y | Sweep the wedge angle =θ= from 0 to 2π              |
| Left-drag &mdash; screen-X | Scale the cylinder height (symmetric around anchor) |
| Right-drag on handle       | Translate the cut volume along the =z= axis         |
| Scroll over handle         | (reserved &mdash; no effect in the current build)   |

See [[UserInterface][User Interface]] for the corresponding buttons,
panels and the full slicer description.

